name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.reduce.shuffle.retry-delay.max.ms
description:
The maximum number of ms the reducer will delay before retrying
  to download map data.

name: hadoop.zk.num-retries
description: Number of tries to connect to ZooKeeper.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.pathcache.expire-after-access-minutes
description:
The length of time after an entry is last accessed that it
    should be automatically removed.

name: dfs.client.read.shortcircuit.streams.cache.expiry.ms
description:
This controls the minimum amount of time
    file descriptors need to sit in the client cache context
    before they can be closed for being inactive for too long.

name: dfs.namenode.blockreport.max.lock.hold.time
description: The BlockReportProcessingThread max write lock hold time in ms.
